 100    def multi_pred_analysis_structure_analysis_next_2(self) -> None:
 101        """Shows the gui elements to select the chains in protein 1."""
 102        self._view.wait_spinner.start()
 103        tmp_proteins_to_predict: list[str] = []
 104        for i in range(self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.rowCount()):
 105            tmp_proteins_to_predict.append(
 106                self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.verticalHeaderItem(i).text(),
 107            )
 108        self._active_task = tasks.Task(
 109            target=main_presenter_async.check_chains_for_subsequent_analysis,
 110            args=(
 111                self._view.ui.box_pred_analysis_multi_prot_struct_1.currentText(),
 112                self._view.ui.box_pred_analysis_multi_prot_struct_2.currentText(),
 113                self._interface_manager.get_current_project(),
 114                tmp_proteins_to_predict,
 115            ),
 116            post_func=self.__await_multi_pred_analysis_structure_analysis_next_2,
 117        )
 118        self._active_task.start()
 119

 220    def _init_multi_pred_analysis_page(self) -> None:

 246    def display_multimer_pred_analysis(self) -> None:
 247        """Displays the multimer prediction + analysis page."""
 248        self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_multi_go_analysis_setup.setText("Predict")
 249        self._view.ui.lbl_pred_analysis_multi_to_analysis_setup.setText("Protein Structure(s)")
 250        # checks internet connection
 251        if not tools.check_internet_connectivity():
 252            gui_utils.no_internet_dialog()
 253            return
 254
 255        self._init_multi_pred_analysis_page()
 256        self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.clear()
 257        self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.setHorizontalHeaderItem(
 258            0,
 259            QtWidgets.QTableWidgetItem("Chain"),
 260        )

 262            1,
 263            QtWidgets.QTableWidgetItem("Sequence"),
 264        )
 265        self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.resizeColumnsToContents()
 266        gui_elements_to_show = [
 267            self._view.ui.lbl_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict,
 268            self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict,
 269            self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict_add,
 270        ]
 271        gui_elements_to_hide = [
 272            self._view.ui.checkbox_add_analysis,
 273            self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict_remove,
 274            self._view.ui.lbl_pred_analysis_multi_prot_name,
 275            self._view.ui.txt_pred_analysis_multi_prot_name,
 276            self._view.ui.lbl_pred_analysis_multi_prot_name_status,
 277            self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_multi_back,
 278            self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_multi_next,
 279            self._view.ui.lbl_pred_analysis_multi_prot_seq,
 280            self._view.ui.txt_pred_analysis_multi_prot_seq,
 281            self._view.ui.lbl_pred_analysis_multi_prot_seq_status,
 282            self._view.ui.lbl_pred_multi_prot_seq_add_2,
 283            self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_multi_prot_seq_add,
 284            self._view.ui.lbl_pred_analysis_multi_prot_seq_overview,
 285            self._view.ui.list_pred_analysis_multi_prot_seq_overview,

 303    def show_prediction_configuration(self) -> None:
 304        """Opens the prediction configuration dialog window."""
 305        config = dialog_advanced_prediction_configurations.DialogAdvancedPredictionConfigurations(
 306            self.prediction_configuration,
 307        )
 308        config.exec_()
 309        self.prediction_configuration.amber_force_field = config.prediction_config.amber_force_field
 310        self.prediction_configuration.templates = config.prediction_config.templates
 311
 312    def check_if_prediction_and_analysis_should_be_done(self):
 313        if self._view.ui.checkbox_add_analysis.isChecked():
 314            self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_multi_go_analysis_setup.setText("Go")
 315            self._view.ui.lbl_pred_analysis_multi_to_analysis_setup.setText("To Analysis Setup")
 316        else:
 317            self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_multi_go_analysis_setup.setText("Predict")
 318            self._view.ui.lbl_pred_analysis_multi_to_analysis_setup.setText("Protein Structure(s)")

 321    def multi_pred_analysis_validate_protein_name(self) -> None:
 322        """Validates the input of the protein name in real-time."""
 323        if safeguard.Safeguard.check_if_value_is_in_table_v_header(
 324                self._view.ui.txt_pred_analysis_multi_prot_name.text(),
 325                self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict,
 326        ):
 327            self._view.ui.lbl_pred_analysis_multi_prot_name_status.setText("Protein name already used.")
 328            self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_multi_next.setEnabled(False)
 329        else:
 330            self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_multi_next.setEnabled(True)
 331            tools.validate_protein_name(
 332                self._view.ui.txt_pred_analysis_multi_prot_name,
 333                self._view.ui.lbl_pred_analysis_multi_prot_name_status,
 334                self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_multi_next,
 335            )
 336
 337    def multi_pred_analysis_validate_protein_sequence(self) -> None:
 338        """Validates the input of the protein sequence in real-time."""
 339        tools.validate_protein_sequence(
 340            self._view.ui.txt_pred_analysis_multi_prot_seq,
 341            self._view.ui.lbl_pred_analysis_multi_prot_seq_status,
 342            self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_multi_prot_seq_add,
 343        )
 344
 345    def multi_pred_analysis_check_if_list_is_empty(self) -> None:
 346        """Checks if the list of sequences of the protein is empty."""
 347        if self._view.ui.list_pred_analysis_multi_prot_seq_overview.count() == 0:
 348            self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict_add_2.setEnabled(False)
 349        else:
 350            self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict_add_2.setEnabled(True)
 351
 352    def multi_pred_analysis_add_sequence_to_list(self) -> None:
 353        """Adds the entered sequence to the sequences of the protein."""
 354        self._view.ui.list_pred_analysis_multi_prot_seq_overview.addItem(
 355            QtWidgets.QListWidgetItem(self._view.ui.txt_pred_analysis_multi_prot_seq.toPlainText()),
 356        )
 357        self.multi_pred_analysis_check_if_list_is_empty()
 358
 359    def multi_pred_analysis_remove_sequence_to_list(self) -> None:
 360        """Removes the entered sequence from the sequences of the protein."""
 361        self._view.ui.list_pred_analysis_multi_prot_seq_overview.takeItem(
 362            self._view.ui.list_pred_analysis_multi_prot_seq_overview.currentRow(),
 363        )
 364        self.multi_pred_analysis_check_if_list_is_empty()
 365        self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_multi_prot_seq_overview_remove.setEnabled(False)
 366

 437    def multi_pred_analysis_add_protein_to_predict(self) -> None:
 438        """Adds the proteins to the list of proteins to predict."""
 439        for i in range(self._view.ui.list_pred_analysis_multi_prot_seq_overview.count()):
 440            self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.setRowCount(
 441                self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.rowCount() + 1,
 442            )
 443            self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.insertRow(
 444                self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.rowCount() + 1,
 445            )
 446            tmp_chain_seq = (
 447                constants.chain_dict.get(i),
 448                self._view.ui.list_pred_analysis_multi_prot_seq_overview.item(i).text(),
 449            )
 450            self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.setItem(
 451                self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.rowCount() - 1,
 452                0,
 453                QtWidgets.QTableWidgetItem(tmp_chain_seq[0]),
 454            )
 455            self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.setItem(
 456                self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.rowCount() - 1,
 457                1,
 458                QtWidgets.QTableWidgetItem(tmp_chain_seq[1]),
 459            )
 460            name_item = QtWidgets.QTableWidgetItem(self._view.ui.txt_pred_analysis_multi_prot_name.text())
 461            self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.setVerticalHeaderItem(
 462                self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.rowCount() - 1,
 463                name_item,
 464            )
 465        self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.resizeColumnsToContents()
 466        self.multi_pred_analysis_check_if_table_is_empty()
 467        self._view.ui.checkbox_add_analysis.show()
 468        self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict_remove.setEnabled(False)
 469
 470    def multi_pred_analysis_remove_protein_to_predict(self) -> None:
 471        """Removes the selected protein from the list of proteins to predict."""
 472        if self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.rowCount() == 1:
 473            self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.removeRow(0)
 474        else:
 475            self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.removeRow(
 476                self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.currentRow(),
 477            )
 478            prot_name = self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.verticalHeaderItem(
 479                self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.currentRow(),
 480            ).text()
 481            for i in range(self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.rowCount()):
 482                if self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.verticalHeaderItem(
 483                        i).text() == prot_name:
 484                    self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.setItem(
 485                        i,
 486                        0,
 487                        QtWidgets.QTableWidgetItem(constants.chain_dict.get(i)),
 488                    )
 489        self.multi_pred_analysis_check_if_table_is_empty()
 490        self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict_remove.setEnabled(False)

 117            post_func=self.__await_multi_pred_analysis_structure_analysis_next_2,
 118        )
 119        self._active_task.start()

 438    def multi_pred_analysis_add_protein_to_predict(self) -> None:
 439        """Adds the proteins to the list of proteins to predict."""
 440        for i in range(self._view.ui.list_pred_analysis_multi_prot_seq_overview.count()):
 441            self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.setRowCount(
 442                self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.rowCount() + 1,
 443            )
 444            self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.insertRow(
 445                self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.rowCount() + 1,
 446            )
 447            tmp_chain_seq = (
 448                constants.chain_dict.get(i),
 449                self._view.ui.list_pred_analysis_multi_prot_seq_overview.item(i).text(),
 450            )
 451            self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.setItem(
 452                self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.rowCount() - 1,
 453                0,
 454                QtWidgets.QTableWidgetItem(tmp_chain_seq[0]),
 455            )
 456            self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.setItem(
 457                self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.rowCount() - 1,
 458                1,
 459                QtWidgets.QTableWidgetItem(tmp_chain_seq[1]),
 460            )
 461            name_item = QtWidgets.QTableWidgetItem(self._view.ui.txt_pred_analysis_multi_prot_name.text())
 462            self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.setVerticalHeaderItem(
 463                self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.rowCount() - 1,
 464                name_item,
 465            )
 466        self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.resizeColumnsToContents()
 467        self.multi_pred_analysis_check_if_table_is_empty()
 468        self._view.ui.checkbox_add_analysis.show()
 469        self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict_remove.setEnabled(False)
 470
 471    def multi_pred_analysis_remove_protein_to_predict(self) -> None:
 472        """Removes the selected protein from the list of proteins to predict."""
 473        if self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.rowCount() == 1:
 474            self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.removeRow(0)
 475        else:
 476            self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.removeRow(
 477                self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.currentRow(),
 478            )
 479            prot_name = self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.verticalHeaderItem(
 480                self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.currentRow(),
 481            ).text()
 482            for i in range(self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.rowCount()):
 483                if self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.verticalHeaderItem(
 484                        i).text() == prot_name:
 485                    self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.setItem(
 486                        i,
 487                        0,
 488                        QtWidgets.QTableWidgetItem(constants.chain_dict.get(i)),
 489                    )
 490        self.multi_pred_analysis_check_if_table_is_empty()
 491        self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict_remove.setEnabled(False)

 671    def switch_multimer_pred_analysis_tab(self) -> None:
 672        """Switches the tabs from prediction to analysis and vice versa."""
 673        if self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_multi_go_analysis_setup.text() == "Predict":
 674            tmp_prediction_runs: list[
 675                prediction_protein_info.PredictionProteinInfo

 677                self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict)
 678            self._view.close()
 679            self.job_input.emit(("job_input", tmp_prediction_runs, self.prediction_configuration, False))
 680        else:
 681            if self._view.ui.tabWidget_2.currentIndex() == 0:

def multi_pred_analysis_add_protein_to_predict(self) -> None: 
438    def multi_pred_analysis_add_protein_to_predict(self) -> None:
439        """Adds the proteins to the list of proteins to predict."""
440        for i in range(self._view.ui.list_pred_analysis_multi_prot_seq_overview.count()):
441            self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.setRowCount(
442                self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.rowCount() + 1,
443            )
444            self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.insertRow(
445                self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.rowCount() + 1,
446            )
447            tmp_chain_seq = (
448                constants.chain_dict.get(i),
449                self._view.ui.list_pred_analysis_multi_prot_seq_overview.item(i).text(),
450            )
451            self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.setItem(
452                self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.rowCount() - 1,
453                0,
454                QtWidgets.QTableWidgetItem(tmp_chain_seq[0]),
455            )
456            self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.setItem(
457                self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.rowCount() - 1,
458                1,
459                QtWidgets.QTableWidgetItem(tmp_chain_seq[1]),
460            )
461            name_item = QtWidgets.QTableWidgetItem(self._view.ui.txt_pred_analysis_multi_prot_name.text())
462            self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.setVerticalHeaderItem(
463                self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.rowCount() - 1,
464                name_item,
465            )
466        self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.resizeColumnsToContents()
467        self.multi_pred_analysis_check_if_table_is_empty()
468        self._view.ui.checkbox_add_analysis.show()
469        self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict_remove.setEnabled(False)

def multi_pred_analysis_remove_protein_to_predict(self) -> None: 
471    def multi_pred_analysis_remove_protein_to_predict(self) -> None:
472        """Removes the selected protein from the list of proteins to predict."""
473        if self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.rowCount() == 1:
474            self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.removeRow(0)
475        else:
476            self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.removeRow(
477                self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.currentRow(),
478            )
479            prot_name = self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.verticalHeaderItem(
480                self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.currentRow(),
481            ).text()
482            for i in range(self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.rowCount()):
483                if self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.verticalHeaderItem(
484                        i).text() == prot_name:
485                    self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict.setItem(
486                        i,
487                        0,
488                        QtWidgets.QTableWidgetItem(constants.chain_dict.get(i)),
489                    )
490        self.multi_pred_analysis_check_if_table_is_empty()
491        self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_multi_prot_to_predict_remove.setEnabled(False)
